00:34:25,355 --> 00:34:28,567
Pergilah ke Pyongyang dan hajar dia.

545
00:34:29,776 --> 00:34:30,694
Kau lihat,

546
00:34:31,319 --> 00:34:33,780
aku tak perlu berdandan
untuk membuatnya sadar.

547
00:34:34,614 --> 00:34:36,825
Begitu kami bertemu kemarin,

548
00:34:37,200 --> 00:34:39,661
